253
00:15:21,630 --> 00:15:24,758
<i>However, it's only canceled
with respect to the director.</i>

254
00:15:24,883 --> 00:15:27,886
<i>We'll now trade the notebook...
for Sayu Yagami.</i>

255
00:15:31,974 --> 00:15:34,101
<i>You're the deputy director
of the NPA...</i>

256
00:15:34,643 --> 00:15:36,854
<i>...so it would be ridiculous for me
to tell you not to alert the police.</i>

257
00:15:37,062 --> 00:15:39,356
<i>But I'd like it if you
move on this on your own.</i>

258
00:15:39,857 --> 00:15:43,819
<i>I'll kill your daughter if I see
the police making too much noise.</i>

259
00:15:44,695 --> 00:15:47,781
<i>That's right...
just like we killed the director,</i>

260
00:15:48,699 --> 00:15:51,577
<i>I'll send you a picture of
Takimura's corpse.</i>

261
00:15:52,327 --> 00:15:53,328
<i>Take a good long look.</i>

262
00:15:54,204 --> 00:15:55,706
<i>I'll contact you tomorrow.</i>

263
00:15:56,248 --> 00:15:57,249
H-Hey!

264
00:15:59,084 --> 00:16:00,127
<i>They got me...</i>

265
00:16:00,752 --> 00:16:02,754
<i>They used the death of the director
as an opportunity to get Sayu...</i>

266
00:16:04,423 --> 00:16:07,718
Light, things are
getting fun again!

267
00:16:08,135 --> 00:16:09,178
Sir...

268
00:16:10,596 --> 00:16:11,555
Why would they
go this far. . .?

269
00:16:11,638 --> 00:16:12,681
Damn it...!

270
00:16:12,764 --> 00:16:16,143
YAGAMI

271
