Dear, you never call from
your work phone...

272
00:16:20,981 --> 00:16:22,524
Huh? Sayu?

273
00:16:23,567 --> 00:16:24,610
<i>Who knows?</i>

274
00:16:24,693 --> 00:16:26,570
<i>Come to think of it, she's late.</i>

275
00:16:28,447 --> 00:16:29,448
Sayu...

276
00:16:30,073 --> 00:16:32,075
