277
00:16:35,287 --> 00:16:36,663
Dad, are you all right?

278
00:16:39,875 --> 00:16:43,045
I think that it was Kira
who killed the director,

279
00:16:43,128 --> 00:16:44,796
not the kidnappers.

280
00:16:44,880 --> 00:16:45,714
