I make sure my daughter's safe.

317
00:18:39,578 --> 00:18:40,746
Let me hear her voice!

318
00:18:40,912 --> 00:18:42,497
<i>All right, all right.</i>

319
00:18:42,581 --> 00:18:44,750
<i>I'll send you another picture.</i>

320
